 in like and - when I got them - me father used to sell nuts and bolts and that, an ironmongery shop you see, and - asked him if I could have a bolt for the spindle for to put the pram wheel into the frame of the bike. He says, oh
 yes. So I got a bolt two inches long, quarter thick or something, put them in. He would see that they were thick enough like, he'd ask you, let's have a look, aye, that's thick enough. Put that in. Then I would - have a bit muck }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
