\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4870305 RA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11413802\charrsid15818556 Just like I have now. That's right.
