\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10813999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11413802\charrsid15818556 Did you have anything to drink with your dinner at work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4870305 RA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11413802\charrsid15818556 Oh yes, tea, we used to make tea, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10813999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11413802\charrsid15818556 Did you have anything to drink with your dinner at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4870305 RA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11413802\charrsid15818556 Tea. Tea, tea, tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10813999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11413802\charrsid15818556 Do you know what your wife and children had for dinner when you were at work?
