\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10813999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11413802\charrsid15818556 Corned beef sandwiches?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4870305 RA  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11413802\charrsid15818556 Yes.
